---
// Installation guide component
---

<section id="installation" class="installation-section compact-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Quick Start Guide</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Get up and running in 5-10 minutes</p>

    <div class="install-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Download Zipy</h3>
          <p>Get the installer for your operating system from the download section above.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Install</h3>
          <div class="platform-tabs">
            <details>
              <summary><strong>ü™ü Windows</strong></summary>
              <ol>
                <li>Double-click the <code>.exe</code> file</li>
                <li>Click "More info" if Windows Defender appears</li>
                <li>Click "Run anyway"</li>
                <li>Follow the installation wizard</li>
              </ol>
              <p class="note">Note: Windows version has UI only (no speech recognition)</p>
            </details>

            <details>
              <summary><strong>üçé macOS (Apple Silicon)</strong></summary>
              <ol>
                <li>Open the <code>.dmg</code> file</li>
                <li>Drag Zipy to Applications folder</li>
                <li><strong>Right-click</strong> Zipy and select "Open" (first time only)</li>
                <li>Click "Open" in the security dialog</li>
              </ol>
              <p class="note">Supported: M1, M2, M3, M4 chips only</p>
            </details>

            <details>
              <summary><strong>üêß Linux (Ubuntu/Debian)</strong></summary>
              <pre><code>sudo dpkg -i zipy_0.1.0_amd64.deb</code></pre>
              <p>Then launch from applications menu or run <code>zipy</code> in terminal.</p>
            </details>

            <details>
              <summary><strong>üêß Linux (AppImage)</strong></summary>
              <pre><code>chmod +x zipy_0.1.0_amd64.AppImage
./zipy_0.1.0_amd64.AppImage</code></pre>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Download Voice Model</h3>
          <p>Download the English speech recognition model (322 MB, one-time):</p>
          <a href="https://april.sapples.net/" target="_blank" class="model-link">
            Download april-english-dev-01110_en.april ‚Üí
          </a>
          <p class="note">Save it to Documents folder for easy access</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Configure Model</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>Open Zipy</li>
            <li>Click Settings (‚öôÔ∏è gear icon)</li>
            <li>Click "Browse" next to ASR Model</li>
            <li>Select the <code>.april</code> file you downloaded</li>
            <li>Click "Save"</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">5</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Start Using!</h3>
          <p>Click "Start" and begin speaking. Your words will appear in real-time!</p>
          <div class="feature-highlights">
            <span>‚úì Speech-to-text</span>
            <span>‚úì AI summaries</span>
            <span>‚úì Export transcripts</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
      <h3>Need Help?</h3>
      <p>Check out the full documentation on <a href="https://github.com/minhtranin/zigy#-installation-guide-for-everyone" target="_blank">GitHub</a> or <a href="https://github.com/minhtranin/zigy/issues" target="_blank">report an issue</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .installation-section {
    background: white;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #4B5563;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .install-steps {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6C5CE7 0%, #5A4BD8 100%);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .step-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #111827;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: #4B5563;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .platform-tabs details {
    background: #F9FAFB;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }

  .platform-tabs summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .platform-tabs summary:hover {
    background: rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.1);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .platform-tabs ol {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .platform-tabs li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #4B5563;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  code, pre {
    background: #1F2937;
    color: #F9FAFB;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  pre {
    padding: 1rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  pre code {
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .note {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #9CA3AF;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .model-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: #6C5CE7;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .model-link:hover {
    background: #5A4BD8;
  }

  .feature-highlights {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-highlights span {
    background: #EDEBFF;
    color: #6C5CE7;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .help-section {
    background: #F9FAFB;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }

  .help-section h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #111827;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .help-section a {
    color: #6C5CE7;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .help-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .step {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .help-section {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
